1
00:00:11,694 --> 00:00:14,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're wobbling a little.</b></font>

2
00:00:14,364 --> 00:00:15,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't help it.</b></font>

3
00:00:15,694 --> 00:00:19,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yesterday's snow is frozen on the road.</b></font>

4
00:00:19,204 --> 00:00:22,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess studless tires don't cut it.</b></font>

5
00:00:30,214 --> 00:00:31,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

6
00:00:34,214 --> 00:00:37,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's up with that car?
It had studless tires, too.</b></font>

7
00:00:41,624 --> 00:00:43,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unbelievable.</b></font>

8
00:00:48,294 --> 00:00:52,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Watch out! Watch it! Oh, no!</b></font>

9
00:00:58,474 --> 00:01:01,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not again! Go right, right!</b></font>

10
00:01:01,474 --> 00:01:05,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, no... Ouch!</b></font>

11
00:01:05,914 --> 00:01:08,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>- Sayuki?
- That hurt!</b></font>

12
00:01:08,814 --> 00:01:11,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This snow is frozen solid.</b></font>

13
00:01:11,324 --> 00:01:14,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You okay, Sayuki?</b></font>

14
00:01:24,364 --> 00:01:28,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Sentimental White"</b></font>

15
00:01:33,344 --> 00:01:36,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is so annoying.</b></font>

16
00:01:36,274 --> 00:01:38,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We started snowboarding at the same time,</b></font>

17
00:01:38,344 --> 00:01:41,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so why are you so good at it already?</b></font>

18
00:01:42,714 --> 00:01:44,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hate to admit it,</b></font>

19
00:01:44,124 --> 00:01:48,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but other girls don't have your athletic talent.</b></font>

20
00:01:48,224 --> 00:01:50,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was the same when you
were learning how to drift.</b></font>

21
00:01:50,964 --> 00:01:55,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You have great intuition
and develop so quickly.</b></font>

22
00:01:59,764 --> 00:02:01,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's Shingo!</b></font>

23
00:02:01,534 --> 00:02:04,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, Sayuki?</b></font>

24
00:02:04,944 --> 00:02:06,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Long time no see!</b></font>

25
00:02:06,274 --> 00:02:09,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What a coincidence to run into you here!</b></font>

26
00:02:09,274 --> 00:02:12,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I never knew you snowboarded.</b></font>

27
00:02:12,714 --> 00:02:15,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, sure!</b></font>

28
00:02:15,284 --> 00:02:17,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, really?</b></font>

29
00:02:19,884 --> 00:02:23,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know how to snowboard!</b></font>

30
00:02:23,724 --> 00:02:26,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And Shingo always had</b></font>

31
00:02:26,094 --> 00:02:28,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>snot dripping from his nose
in elementary school!</b></font>

32
00:02:28,764 --> 00:02:30,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shut up!</b></font>

33
00:02:30,094 --> 00:02:32,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Everyone teased him by
calling him "Drippy-Nose Shingo,"</b></font>

34
00:02:32,804 --> 00:02:37,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so he turned bad and became a rebel racer!</b></font>

35
00:02:37,304 --> 00:02:39,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't make stuff up, Sayuki!</b></font>

36
00:02:39,844 --> 00:02:43,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just had a cold that day. That's all.</b></font>

37
00:02:45,814 --> 00:02:48,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Mako, don't you wanna
snowboard some more?</b></font>

38
00:02:48,654 --> 00:02:50,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>- What?
- Go right ahead.</b></font>

39
00:02:50,984 --> 00:02:54,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll be talking to Shingo
about the good old days.</b></font>

40
00:02:54,654 --> 00:02:57,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, why don't you go with her?</b></font>

41
00:02:59,164 --> 00:03:01,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

42
00:03:01,694 --> 00:03:04,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

43
00:03:04,304 --> 00:03:06,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No problem.</b></font>

44
00:03:10,134 --> 00:03:11,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you think of him?</b></font>

45
00:03:11,704 --> 00:03:13,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He looks wimpy,</b></font>

46
00:03:13,544 --> 00:03:17,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but he seems pretty normal
for a friend of yours.</b></font>

47
00:03:17,144 --> 00:03:19,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How's his driving?</b></font>

48
00:03:19,144 --> 00:03:21,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's one of the faster
drivers of the Night Kids.</b></font>

49
00:03:21,684 --> 00:03:26,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Of course, he's not nearly as fast
as "Impact Blue," Usui's fastest.</b></font>

50
00:03:30,664 --> 00:03:34,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, she's too cute
not to have a boyfriend.</b></font>

51
00:03:34,794 --> 00:03:38,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You should've set me up with her instead.</b></font>

52
00:03:38,004 --> 00:03:41,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't be stupid!
You're not good enough for her.</b></font>

53
00:03:41,834 --> 00:03:43,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By the way,</b></font>

54
00:03:43,174 --> 00:03:46,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>don't let them find out that
this is a blind date, okay?</b></font>

55
00:03:46,374 --> 00:03:49,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She would kill me if she knew.</b></font>

56
00:03:49,044 --> 00:03:50,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't worry.</b></font>

57
00:03:50,884 --> 00:03:55,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By the way, what about you, Sayuki?</b></font>

58
00:03:55,214 --> 00:03:56,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

59
00:03:56,654 --> 00:03:58,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nakazato from the other night.</b></font>

60
00:03:58,654 --> 00:04:02,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think he has a crush on you.</b></font>

61
00:04:23,674 --> 00:04:26,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're good. When did
you start snowboarding?</b></font>

62
00:04:26,544 --> 00:04:29,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>- Last year.
- That's amazing.</b></font>

63
00:04:29,214 --> 00:04:34,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Very few girls could go
that fast on this hard snow.</b></font>

64
00:04:34,924 --> 00:04:38,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's exciting and a lot of fun.</b></font>

65
00:04:38,464 --> 00:04:42,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I get into something,
I'm totally focused.</b></font>

66
00:04:55,944 --> 00:05:00,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, Mako, what do you
think of Shingo's friend?</b></font>

67
00:05:00,484 --> 00:05:02,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know.</b></font>

68
00:05:02,814 --> 00:05:07,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's pleasant, and seems
like the serious type.</b></font>

69
00:05:07,494 --> 00:05:10,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>- Is that it?
- What do you mean, is that it?</b></font>

70
00:05:10,794 --> 00:05:14,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just met him, so I don't really know.</b></font>

71
00:05:14,494 --> 00:05:16,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Aha!</i></b></font>

72
00:05:16,134 --> 00:05:18,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I sense some chemistry between them.</i></b></font>

73
00:05:18,964 --> 00:05:20,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By the way,</b></font>

74
00:05:20,304 --> 00:05:23,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard something interesting the other day.</b></font>

75
00:05:23,304 --> 00:05:26,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke Takahashi of the
Red Suns is recruiting racers,</b></font>

76
00:05:26,804 --> 00:05:31,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>including Akina's Eight-Six,
to build a new team.</b></font>

77
00:05:31,584 --> 00:05:35,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hear it'll be a special traveling team.</b></font>

78
00:05:37,114 --> 00:05:39,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that true, Sayuki?</b></font>

79
00:05:39,784 --> 00:05:43,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I admire them for thinking
of a concept like that.</b></font>

80
00:05:43,124 --> 00:05:46,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They never stay in one place.</b></font>

81
00:05:46,324 --> 00:05:48,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They always keep moving forward.</b></font>

82
00:05:50,164 --> 00:05:53,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're so awesome that I almost hate them.</b></font>

83
00:05:53,664 --> 00:05:55,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They truly have charisma.</b></font>

84
00:05:57,844 --> 00:06:00,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wish I could see Takumi again.</b></font>

85
00:06:00,844 --> 00:06:04,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder how he's doing.</b></font>

86
00:06:04,014 --> 00:06:07,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I bet he looks handsome.</b></font>

87
00:06:07,654 --> 00:06:09,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm never wrong about things like that.</b></font>

88
00:06:09,784 --> 00:06:13,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, sure, Sayuki.</b></font>

89
00:06:13,054 --> 00:06:17,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, man, I'm getting kind of fired up.</b></font>

90
00:06:17,664 --> 00:06:21,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, the road on the way here</b></font>

91
00:06:21,034 --> 00:06:23,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>looked kind of nice.</b></font>

92
00:06:23,194 --> 00:06:26,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no snow down at the bottom.</b></font>

93
00:06:26,704 --> 00:06:29,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was thinking the same thing.</b></font>

94
00:06:29,074 --> 00:06:31,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wanna check it out later?</b></font>

95
00:06:31,674 --> 00:06:34,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>God, we love racing, don't we?</b></font>

96
00:06:36,314 --> 00:06:37,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

97
00:06:40,484 --> 00:06:42,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm so bored.</b></font>

98
00:06:42,584 --> 00:06:45,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The pass is snowy.</b></font>

99
00:06:45,684 --> 00:06:46,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke...</b></font>

100
00:06:46,984 --> 00:06:50,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Those who conquer winter conquer summer.</b></font>

101
00:06:51,994 --> 00:06:55,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our project won't start until this spring.</b></font>

102
00:06:55,434 --> 00:06:58,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But we won't make any progress</b></font>

103
00:06:58,104 --> 00:07:01,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>if we just sit around all winter.</b></font>

104
00:07:01,104 --> 00:07:03,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go drive on the snowy road.</b></font>

105
00:07:03,034 --> 00:07:04,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

106
00:07:04,344 --> 00:07:08,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just clear your mind and drive
on the slippery, frozen road,</b></font>

107
00:07:08,344 --> 00:07:10,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>day in and day out.</b></font>

108
00:07:13,444 --> 00:07:16,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'll see the effect in the spring,</b></font>

109
00:07:16,614 --> 00:07:20,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>when you change back to high-grip tires.</b></font>

110
00:07:20,454 --> 00:07:22,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your senses will be sharper,</b></font>

111
00:07:22,124 --> 00:07:26,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and your driving skills
will be dramatically refined.</b></font>

112
00:07:27,364 --> 00:07:28,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke...</b></font>

113
00:07:28,694 --> 00:07:33,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll create a new
unbeatable record at each pass</b></font>

114
00:07:33,364 --> 00:07:35,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and build our legend.</b></font>

115
00:07:35,034 --> 00:07:37,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

116
00:07:37,034 --> 00:07:39,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The snow is not a handicap.</b></font>

117
00:07:39,044 --> 00:07:41,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's your best training partner.</b></font>

118
00:07:41,914 --> 00:07:45,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Racers don't have an off season.</b></font>

119
00:07:45,414 --> 00:07:46,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right.</b></font>

120
00:07:58,064 --> 00:08:00,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Studless tires don't grip as much.</b></font>

121
00:08:00,624 --> 00:08:03,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But this is good training.</b></font>

122
00:08:03,064 --> 00:08:05,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A corner is there, so you attack it.</b></font>

123
00:08:05,834 --> 00:08:08,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the racer's instinct.</b></font>

124
00:08:13,144 --> 00:08:14,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's up with that car?!</b></font>

125
00:08:14,974 --> 00:08:18,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That was a Sileighty.
Where did it come from?</b></font>

126
00:08:20,614 --> 00:08:22,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow, the driver is very skilled!</b></font>

127
00:08:26,284 --> 00:08:27,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How is it?</b></font>

128
00:08:27,454 --> 00:08:31,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>These are all one-pattern, mid-speed corners,</b></font>

129
00:08:31,094 --> 00:08:32,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so it's boring.</b></font>

130
00:08:32,694 --> 00:08:35,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I like Usui Pass the best.</b></font>

131
00:08:42,804 --> 00:08:44,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello?</b></font>

132
00:08:44,304 --> 00:08:46,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Shingo, what's up?</b></font>

133
00:08:47,844 --> 00:08:48,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

134
00:08:48,974 --> 00:08:51,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They've been seeing each other?</b></font>

135
00:08:51,784 --> 00:08:54,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, he was all excited.</b></font>

136
00:08:54,454 --> 00:08:56,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think they have a date today.</b></font>

137
00:08:56,384 --> 00:08:59,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, really? I had no idea.</b></font>

138
00:09:01,324 --> 00:09:05,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's good. Christmas is coming up soon.</b></font>

139
00:09:05,994 --> 00:09:08,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. Talk to you later.</b></font>

140
00:09:12,834 --> 00:09:15,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I wonder if Mako's many</i>
<i>years without a boyfriend</i></b></font>

141
00:09:15,834 --> 00:09:18,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>are finally coming to an end.</i></b></font>

142
00:09:20,844 --> 00:09:25,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think this SW20 is a very good car.</b></font>

143
00:09:25,244 --> 00:09:29,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A two-seater is fun, but it's inconvenient.</b></font>

144
00:09:29,654 --> 00:09:34,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm thinking of buying something
more practical next time.</b></font>

145
00:09:34,394 --> 00:09:37,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe a 4WD wagon.</b></font>

146
00:09:37,194 --> 00:09:40,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you quitting racing?</b></font>

147
00:09:40,424 --> 00:09:42,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think so, yeah.</b></font>

148
00:09:49,274 --> 00:09:54,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not making any excuses,
but I think I've had enough fun.</b></font>

149
00:09:54,244 --> 00:09:58,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When you're a beginner,
you just try your hardest,</b></font>

150
00:09:58,444 --> 00:10:01,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and it's exciting to see yourself progress.</b></font>

151
00:10:03,214 --> 00:10:07,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But when you get to a certain level,
you kind of see your limits.</b></font>

152
00:10:07,224 --> 00:10:11,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You stop having goals and become less eager.</b></font>

153
00:10:12,864 --> 00:10:18,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess that's how everyone grows out of it.</b></font>

154
00:10:18,604 --> 00:10:24,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well... I really don't think
one's goals disappear that easily.</b></font>

155
00:10:24,074 --> 00:10:25,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, yeah?</b></font>

156
00:10:25,574 --> 00:10:30,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There was a time when I thought
I would quit racing by this summer.</b></font>

157
00:10:30,714 --> 00:10:33,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I had an opportunity to see</b></font>

158
00:10:33,584 --> 00:10:36,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>a much higher-level racer,</b></font>

159
