171
00:11:49,694 --> 00:11:53,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It might suit you better to get
dressed up and go out during the day,</b></font>

172
00:11:53,824 --> 00:11:55,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>since you're so pretty.</b></font>

173
00:12:12,344 --> 00:12:14,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm serious about this, Mako.</b></font>

174
00:12:14,814 --> 00:12:17,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never liked anyone this much.</b></font>

